81
00:05:11,360 --> 00:05:14,240
[SPEAKER_01] Bio sam poput, što sam odabrao za svoju karijeru?

82
00:05:14,800 --> 00:05:16,319
[SPEAKER_01] Je li ovo ono što ću raditi zauvijek?

83
00:05:16,480 --> 00:05:18,079
