523
00:36:02,800 --> 00:36:04,159
[SPEAKER_00] To je cool, čovječe.

524
00:36:04,239 --> 00:36:04,800
[SPEAKER_01] To je lijepo.

525
00:36:04,880 --> 00:36:08,000
