565
00:39:13,119 --> 00:39:15,840
[SPEAKER_01] Ali, da, samo su to sitne stvari.

566
00:39:15,920 --> 00:39:19,599
[SPEAKER_01] I opet, to je, znaš, to je također malo zakopano, zar ne?

567
00:39:19,679 --> 00:39:22,159
[SPEAKER_01] To je kao da je u postavkama na dnu, zar ne?

568
00:39:22,800 --> 00:39:23,599
[SPEAKER_01] Što je u redu, zar ne?

569
00:39:23,679 --> 00:39:26,880
