575
00:39:54,800 --> 00:39:54,800
[UNKNOWN] Da.

576
00:39:55,599 --> 00:40:00,159
[SPEAKER_01] I istina je, kao što ste upravo rekli, ljudi vas nazivaju po imenu, kao što, oh, hej, Charlie.

577
00:40:00,639 --> 00:40:03,280
[SPEAKER_01] Ljudi to rade i meni putem podrške e-pošte.

578
00:40:03,519 --> 00:40:04,320
[SPEAKER_01] To mi se sviđa.

579
