1202
01:25:20,560 --> 01:25:21,760
[SPEAKER_01] Samo sramite ljude.

1203
01:25:21,920 --> 01:25:22,960
[SPEAKER_01] Da, sjajno.

1204
01:25:23,359 --> 01:25:23,439
[SPEAKER_01] Da.

1205
01:25:23,680 --> 01:25:24,000
